  "message": "\ud83c\udfa8 docs: enlarge ACMM badge logo\n\nTightens the SVG viewBox from 24x24 to 20x20 so the same globe-and-\nstar design fills more of the canvas at shields.io's fixed render\nsize (~14px). Also bumps stroke widths (1.5 \u2192 2 for the globe outer\ncircle, 1.2 \u2192 1.6 for meridians + ellipse) so the strokes stay\ncrisp at the smaller render. Bumped &v=4 to bust GitHub camo.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
